  "remarks": "QDi.064\nTunisian passport number K929139, issued on 14 Feb. 1995, expired on 13 Feb. 2000.\nNational identification number a) 00319547 issued on 08 Dec. 1994. b) Italian Fiscal Code: SSDSBN68B10Z352F.\nMother’s name is Beya Al-Saidani. Deported from Italy to Tunisia on 2 Jun. 2008. Imprisoned in Tunisia in Aug. 2014. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 22 Apr. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 24 Apr. 2002 (amended 10 Apr. 2003, 26 Nov. 2004, 9 Sep. 2005, 20 Dec. 2005 and 7 Jun. 2007, 21 Dec. 2007, 10 Aug 2009, 23 Dec. 2010 and 24 Nov. 2014, 6 Dec 2019, 30 Oct. 2023).",
